{
  "name": "JobHunter(Public)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 🛠️ OPERATION MODE (MODULAR JOB HUNTING ENGINE)\n\nThis workflow is built as a generic template. It runs 3 entirely decoupled pipelines. \n**How to use:** Simply configure the green `[CONFIG]` nodes at the start of each pipeline.\n\n1. **PIPELINE 1: SCRAPER**\n   - Edit `[CONFIG] Job Searches` to paste up to 4 LinkedIn Search URLs.\n   - Runs every 6 hours to fetch, clean, and store raw job data in Google Sheets.\n2. **Google Sheets configuration**\n   - Duplicate the file(https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1blfsmqiBh8pVz7vQzlPFIUEUruvvc9VIKeu5AZsUTHA/edit?usp=sharing)\n   - Setup your Google API key, insert the sheet url.\n\n3. **PIPELINE 2: AI ENRICHMENT & SCORING**\n   - Edit `[CONFIG] Candidate Profile` to define the target skills, deal-breakers, and technical stack for the AI to evaluate.\n   - Runs every 8 hours, processing unchecked rows through the Gemini LLM.\n\n4. **PIPELINE 3: EMAIL DIGEST ALERT**\n   - Edit `[CONFIG] Email Settings` to set the delivery inbox.\n   - Runs daily at 08:00 AM, compiling high-score matches (Score >= 75) into an HTML digest.\n\n",
        "height": 476,
        "width": 720
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1120,
        288
      ],
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "id": "28580358-9810-4765-b6bf-3672f9be2ec6"
    },
